    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies a harmonious balance between performance and value. This unit has been maintained with rigorous attention to mechanical standards, ensuring a confident and composed driving experience. While the vehicle exhibits minor signs of previous stewardship, its structural integrity and interior appointments remain in commendable form. This offering represents a premier opportunity for the professional seeking a reliable, high-caliber automobile at a strategic price point.",
      "price": 29850.0,
